# Referral Campaign Smart Contract

## Setup

### 1. Install SUI binaries

Use the latest release as the tag

```bash
rustup update stable && cargo install --locked --git https://github.com/MystenLabs/sui.git --tag testnet-v1.8.2 sui
```

### 2. Generate deployer wallet

_wip_

### 3. Add RPC

```bash
testnet, devnet or mainnet RPC
```

### 4. Deploy

For example deploy of campaign package

```bash
sui client publish --gas-budget 300000000
```

### 5. Setup package

Check README.md of deployed package for further instructions
